Change MAC Address :-
                    MAC address is divide into three layers
                    * New Mac
                    * Current MAc
                    * Permanent Mac

 When we change mac address first time the mac of new mac layer change when we again change
 mac address the current address is replaced by new mac and new mac newly enter mac is placed.

     To Change MAC : macchanger eth0 -m ( new mac )
                    if we run this command two time then current layer also replaced.

